text: Yeung Man Wai (Chinese: 楊文蔚; born 18 September 1994) is a high jumper from Hong Kong. She won a silver medal at the 2017 Asian Championships and placed fifth at the 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:Hong Kong female high jumpers Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Hong Kong
